Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.gamelogic.effectscreator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EffectsCreator
    Represents all the classes that creates some effects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MoveAndShootCreator
    Sets and creates the effect that moves and shoots a players.
    MoveAnotherPlayerCreator  
    MoveCreator
    Sets and creates the moving effect
    PayCreator
    Creates and sets the effect that makes the player pay.
    ShootAndMarkAOECreator
    Sets and creates the effect that shoots to a player and marks all the other targets.
    ShootAOECreator
    Sets and creates the effect that shoots to all the players in a Square.
    ShootChainCreator
    Sets and creates the chain of shooting effects, used by the T.H.O.R.
    ShootCreator
    Sets and creates the shooting effect.
    ShootCreatorAbstract
    Abstract class that represents the classes that creates a shoot effect.
    ShootDirectionCreator
    Creates and sets the effects that shoots in a single direction.
    ShootRoomCreator
    Sets and creates the effects that shoots to all the players in a room.
    ShootShockWaveCreator
    Creates and sets the effect that shoots around the player to targets on different squares or to all the targets.
    ShootSpawnSquareCreator  
    ShootVortexCreator
    Creates and sets the effect that shoots a vortex.
    Targets
    Support class used by the action manager to see who has been hit during the action.
